Perl-Dist-WiX version 1.102_102

DESCRIPTION
    This package is the upgrade to Perl::Dist based on Windows Installer XML
    technology, instead of Inno Setup.

    Perl distributions built with this module have the option of being
    created as Windows Installer databases (otherwise known as .msi files)

INSTALLATION
    To install this module, run the following commands:

            perl Makefile.PL
            make
            make test
            make install

DEPENDENCIES
    Perl 5.8.1 is the mimimum version of perl that this module will run on.

    Other modules that this module depends on are a working version of
    Alien::WiX, Data::Dump::Streamer 2.08, Data::UUID 1.149,
    Devel::StackTrace 1.20, Exception::Class 1.22, File::ShareDir 1.00,
    IO::String 1.08, List::MoreUtils 0.07, Module::CoreList 2.17,
    Object::InsideOut 3.53, Perl::Dist 1.14, Process 0.26, Readonly 1.03,
    URI 1.35, and Win32 0.35.

